::Eclispe::

    Awaking with a start under a full moon, the Cybertronian y=
outh relized he needed a beast mode. Unfortunatly his DNA scanners were con=
fused. They couldn't pick up any DNA in the area. He was lying on his back,=
 and an energon surge went through his systems. It was minor, due to advanc=
ed Cybertronian Technology. He then noticed a sharp pain in his back. Turni=
ng over he saw part of the Golden Disk.
    "Wow, this is so cool!!" He sai=
d. Another surge went through him. "I'm gonna need a Beast Mode."
    His a=
utosystems once again scanned the area, this time they found something. Onl=
y it wasn't an animal, it was DNA encoded on the Disk. It copied the patter=
n anyway, and started to frame it onto Eclispe's body....
